  "intent": "Execute magnetic bead purification of adapter-ligated cDNA using NEBNext Sample Purification Beads. Add 87\u00b5L beads per sample to 96\u00b5L cDNA reactions, incubate 10 minutes at room temperature with mixing. Engage magnetic separation, remove supernatant, perform two 180\u00b5L 80% ethanol washes with 30-second incubations. Air dry beads, then elute purified cDNA in 17\u00b5L 0.1X TE buffer with 15 cycles of mixing. Transfer 15\u00b5L eluate to chilled output plate at 4\u00b0C for downstream PCR amplification.",
